name: r-soildb
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "2.7.2" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-soildb
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/soilDB_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/soilDB/soilDB_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 001497e78a315094c41315aaac9ff43c9a493c0d7cad1b7e584c5ae2deabd940

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-dbi
    - r-aqp
    - r-curl
    - r-data.table
    - r-plyr
    - r-raster
    - r-reshape2
    - r-sp
    - r-xml2
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-dbi
    - r-aqp
    - r-curl
    - r-data.table
    - r-plyr
    - r-raster
    - r-reshape2
    - r-sp
    - r-xml2

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('soilDB')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('soilDB')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: http://ncss-tech.github.io/AQP/
  license: GPL-3.0-or-later
  summary: A collection of functions for reading data from USDA-NCSS soil databases.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - ocefpaf
    - rvalieris

# Type: Package
